    "#### Universal Function, or ufunc, is a function that performs element-wise operations on ndarrays.<br>Unary ufuncs work on a single ndarry, binary ufuncs work on a pair"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
